rate of return by nearly 62 million the agency reduced the amount 
of the refunds in 1987 
comsat said the commission in effect illegally ordered the 
satellite corporation to reduce its rates retroactively 
the us circuit court of appeals rejected comsats arguments in 
a twopage order last year 
the case is communications satellite corp vs fcc 891687 
