police said in response that they were investigating every 
complaint of brutality a spokeswoman also acknowledged that prison 
conditions need to be improved 
police treat complaints of brutality by officers with special 
seriousness an investigation has been launched into every 
complaint submitted to police said elinoar mazoz who deals with 
