east how much of each remains a question 
the economic merger takes place july 1 when the west german 
mark becomes east germanys currency and east germany abandons its 
communist economics for western capitalism 
the union will enlarge west germanys economy by an estimated 5 
to 10 percent but few statistics are available on the east german 
economy 
experts say unification could help germany sustain growth at the 
current west german level of above 3 percent 
