concern for a priest to the prosecutors office damato said 
at the altar of the 80yearold gothicstyle church where he has 
celebrated mass for 28 years gigante blesses kneeling parishioners 
while ceiling fans stir the air thick gold bracelets hang from the 
priests wrists 
as far as his parishioners are concerned gigante can do little 
wrong and he has ridden out storms that would have sent other 
