dreams of making clothes in poland where his mother was born 
the darling of the daughters of the titled rich starzewskis 
specialty is kicky party clothes and his signature is the 
horizontal pleat 
born and raised in england the 28yearold designer speaks 
fluent polish learned in a polish school and from his parents who 
fled poland in the second world war 
my culture is from my family books music and art without 
doubt its a romanticized picture and some of that feeling comes 
out in my clothes said starzewski peering through stylish 
hornrimmed glasses and a thoroughly european cloud of cigarette 
smoke 
the polish are very much like the french they depend more on 
emotion than logic he said my themes are never based on 
history or culture but rather on mood i do clothes that are 
sensual with a bit of fun 
