maria who spent the war years in a military school after fleeing 
poland 
because of her military training she is good at organizing 
and she runs the shop he said 
she is also a brilliant technician im competing with people 
30 years older but because of her skill our clothes are just as 
well made just as well cut 
miss cierach whose polish father served time in a siberian 
labor camp is famous for having designed the duchess of yorks 
sumptuous satin wedding dress 
her madetoorder evening clothes hang heavy with braid beads 
and brocade her client list is laden with duchesses 
i have a tremendous sense of texture and color an affinity 
for anything ornate she said in a telephone interview from 
dallas where she was fitting her ball gowns to the cream of texas 
society 
