cash or 50 cents a share plus 03 shares of aig common stock the 
amount of aig stock to be exchanged can be adjusted depending on 
aigs share price at the time the deal closes 
ilfcs three controlling owners have agreed to accept aig stock 
for their holdings jacobsen said 
